name: Coomoora  Camel&Black  Lp Cover
description:
Coomoora, is not a brand of bag furthermore, but a simple and original concept which allows to create its bag in its image, according to its musical tastes. 

"Trente Trois Tours" It's a world of possibilities. So now discover&find which LP Cover has been made for you.

The bag has 7 pockets, among which 3 outsides and of a compartment for laptop 15".

-

Coomoora, n’est pas une marque de sac de plus, mais un concept simple et original qui permet de créer son sac à son image, en fonction de ses goûts musicaux.

"Trentre Trois Tours" est un monde de possibilités. Maintenant cherchez&découvrez quelle pochette de vinyle vous correspond le plus.

Le sac dispose de 7 poches, dont 3 extérieurs et d’un compartiment pour laptop 15″.

-

320 x 355 x 100 mm

-

FREE Shipping for France. / Livraison Gratuite en France

-
Lp cover not included / Pochette de vinyle non incluse
